2012-10-12 Eugene Wissner <belka.ew@gmail.com>

	3.6.0-1dl:
	* Added ChangeLog
	* Updated
	* Removed 2.x theme and patches
	* Changed tarball type to .xz
	* Removed --enable-debug flag
	* Removed cxxflags()
	* Added $PKG_GCONFTWO variable to avoid unrecognized
	--disable-schemas-install option and $PKG_SANIFYNOTOUCH
	* Removed "removedir $PKG_STAGEROOT$PKG_SYSCONFDIR/dm" because etc/dm
	doesn't exist after makeinstall()
	* Removed the following files:
		- enlightenment.desktop (isn't shipped with Slackware)
		- xfce.desktop (already included in xfce4-session)
		- gnome.desktop (already included in gnome-session)
	* Updated *.desktop path to the actual usr/share/xsessions
	* Removed from doinst backupfile() function and replaced it with
	dbs' configfile() in build. The main configuration file in gdm3 is
	/etc/custom.conf
	* Added "dconf update" to doinst.sh to recompile dconf settings and to
	apply gdm configuration
